Cell["\<\
Do the Monte Carlo simulation. Without specifying the measurement, all bare \
fermion modes are monitored:\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->1494923699,ExpressionUUID->"dda3a3fb-86c0-405f-823a-a7f8c39c0e5c"],

